---
title: Gourmet Beans and Sausages with goat's cheese and rice
description: This savoury and herbaceous dish is a pleasing mix of subtle flavours and unmistakable tastes. Spoonfuls of fluffy rice are perfect for soaking up every last drop of this rich, hearty bean and sausage stew.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220921_R03_W46_IE_IECFQP0165-1_KB_Main_high-9df46ea6.jpg
